data.description: Welcome to this fantastic investment opportunity located in the popular Security neighborhood.  This home is a true ranch floorplan with two large bedrooms on the Main Level- including a true Master Suite with large closet and attached bathroom!  There is a potential third bedroom on the Main Level that has been converted into a huge Dining Room- that can easily be converted back.  The Basement is finished and can easily bring the property back to over 2100 total square feet!  Vinyl Windows throughout- newer roof- just make it pretty!  The Backyard is one of the biggest in the neighborhood, and from the top of it, offers stunning views.  This home is ripe with opportunity!
